{{Infobox dungeon |name = Rusturf Tunnel |image = [[File:Rusturf Tunnel.png|300px]] |caption = A map of Rusturf Tunnel. |tokens = 14,000 |location = North of Verdanturf Town, east of Route 116. }} '''Rusturf Tunnel''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Hoenn]]. It initially has 49 tiles arranged in a 7x7 square, including 7 chest tiles, 17 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile. Wild Encounters have 400,000 HP.
